snippet.title: RoFIsh: Prelude Gameplay Trailer EN
snippet.description:
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1731230/RoFIsh_Prelude/
RoFIsh: Prelude is a first person adventure about a cat named Stas, trying to escape an island after a shipwreck.
Throughout the game you will get to witness a deliberately clawchéd plot, absurd dialogs and drunkard crabs.
Twitter: https://twitter.com/npukoJITeam
VK GROUP: https://vk.com/npukojiteam
